g.text: This workflow mixes existing KNIME nodes with the new Spark nodes to find the optimal parameters for a k-means clustering using the hillclimbing approach.
+ Spark Job Server needs to be configured in File->Preferences KNIME->Spark
+ Spark Job Server needs to be installed and configured
